WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.460 --> 00:00:02.820
I hurt you so badly, it's excruciating.

2
00:00:02.960 --> 00:00:03.680
Answer me.

3
00:00:04.000 --> 00:00:05.380
He Jiu Ling, you're insane!

4
00:00:05.580 --> 00:00:06.000
Bastard.

5
00:00:11.750 --> 00:00:13.750
Ji Lingling, Ji Lingling.

6
00:00:24.590 --> 00:00:26.730
Sir, Miss Ji must have suffered

7
00:00:26.730 --> 00:00:27.890
a strong mental shock.

8
00:00:28.050 --> 00:00:28.990
Plus physical exhaustion

9
00:00:28.990 --> 00:00:29.690
exceeded her capacity,

10
00:00:29.910 --> 00:00:30.650
that's why she passed out.

11
00:00:30.950 --> 00:00:31.890
As long as she rests well,

12
00:00:32.010 --> 00:00:32.890
she should wake up soon.

13
00:00:32.930 --> 00:00:33.950
How soon is soon?

14
00:00:34.170 --> 00:00:35.050
About one or two days.

15
00:00:35.370 --> 00:00:36.070
These two days,

16
00:00:36.490 --> 00:00:37.830
you must stay at the manor at all times.

17
00:00:38.230 --> 00:00:39.230
If anything happens to her,

18
00:00:39.670 --> 00:00:40.590
you'll pay for it.

19
00:00:41.130 --> 00:00:42.190
Yes, yes, sir.

20
00:00:49.780 --> 00:00:51.740
Ji Lingling, why did you lie to me?

21
00:00:51.800 --> 00:00:52.940
I clearly didn't sleep with her,

22
00:00:53.000 --> 00:00:53.920
Why did you get so drunk?

23
00:00:55.880 --> 00:00:57.340
You deliberately said these things,

24
00:00:57.880 --> 00:00:59.440
trying to get me to let you go.

25
00:01:01.640 --> 00:01:02.760
Let me tell you,

26
00:01:02.980 --> 00:01:04.540
I will never let you go in this life.

27
00:01:05.300 --> 00:01:06.300
Get better soon.

